---
title: "Dialectical Cycle — State Machine"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> ContextRetrieval: New query arrives

    ContextRetrieval --> ThesisGeneration: KG context assembled
    note right of ContextRetrieval
        RL agent performs multi-hop
        think-query-retrieve-rethink
        over knowledge hypergraph
    end note

    ThesisGeneration --> CrossNegation: 2-5 theses generated
    note right of ThesisGeneration
        Heterogeneous models (Claude, GPT-4, Gemini)
        Each declares: categories, causal model,
        falsification criteria, regime assumptions
    end note

    CrossNegation --> ContradictionCrystallization: Negation edges written
    note right of CrossNegation
        Must use typed rewrite operators:
        SPLIT, MERGE, REVERSE, ADD_MEDIATOR,
        SCOPE_TO_REGIME, TEMPORALIZE
    end note

    ContradictionCrystallization --> Sublation: MIS computed
    note right of ContradictionCrystallization
        4 specialized trackers + cross-verification
        Contradictions scored by action-distance
    end note

    Sublation --> MetaReflection: Graph rewrites executed
    note right of Sublation
        2 competing synthesizers
        Cross-negation of syntheses
        Schema induction triggered
    end note

    state MetaReflection {
        [*] --> CheckVelocity
        CheckVelocity --> Progressing: velocity > threshold
        CheckVelocity --> Stalled: velocity < threshold for 2+ cycles
        CheckVelocity --> Stuck: binary oscillation detected

        Progressing --> [*]
        Stalled --> [*]
        Stuck --> ReSpecify: change unit of analysis
        ReSpecify --> [*]
    }

    MetaReflection --> ThesisGeneration: CONTINUE (sublated output becomes new thesis)
    MetaReflection --> RegimeScopedOutput: TERMINATE (contradictions bounded)
    MetaReflection --> ContextRetrieval: RE-SPECIFY (change abstraction level)

    RegimeScopedOutput --> [*]: Deliver policies per regime

    note right of RegimeScopedOutput
        Output: regime-scoped decision policies
        Each policy traces back through
        KG provenance to evidence + episodes
    end note
